n  <- 300
wn <- rnorm(n)            

ma <- numeric(n)
ma[1] <- wn[1]                         
ma[2] <- wn[2] + 0.4*wn[1]
for(i in 3:n){
  ma[i] <- wn[i] + 0.4*wn[i-1] + 0.6*wn[i-2]
}

Karakteristik MA(3)

Plot Time Series

ts.plot(ma)

Terlihat bahwa berdasarkan plot time series, data MA(2) yang dibangkitkan stasioner dalam rataan.

Plot ACF

acf(ma, lag.max = 20)

Terlihat bahwa berdasarkan plot ACF tersebut cuts off di lag setelah kedua.

Plot PACF

pacf(ma)

Terlihat bahwa berdasarkan plot PACF tersebut cenderung tails off.

set.seed(1234)
n1  <- 300
wn <- rnorm(n1)  # white noise ~ N(0,1)

ar <- numeric(n1)
ar[1] <- wn[1]
ar[2] <- wn[2] + 0.5*ar[1]
for (t in 3:n1) {
  ar[t] <- wn[t] + 0.5*ar[t-1] + 0.2*ar[t-2]
}

wn <- rnorm(n)
y <- numeric(n)
y[1:2] <- wn[1:2] 
for (t in 3:n) {
  y[t] <- 0.5*y[t-1] + 0.2*y[t-2] + wn[t] + 0.4*wn[t-1] + 0.6*wn[t-2]
}
